Building LiteCoins on Unbuntu 16.04
(If you want to install on Ubuntu 18.04, you can download litecoins static version on github, https://github.com/chain123-team/litecoins/releases/download/1.3.0.1/litecoins-static-1.3.0.1-arm-linux-gnu-ubuntu.16.0.4.tar.gz)

Use the autogen script to prepare the build environment.

    ./autogen.sh
    ./configure
    make

Always verify the signatures and checksums.

See doc/build-*.md for instructions on building litecoinsd,
the intended-for-services, no-graphical-interface, reference
implementation of LiteCoins.
